{
  "id": "6a242ddb57102a38393391fe",
  "title": "\"概念の出来\" を仕分けるカテゴリ",
  "created": 1780755932,
  "updated": 1780973341,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a242ddb57102a38393391fe",
      "text": "\"概念の出来\" を仕分けるカテゴリ",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1780755932,
      "updated": 1780755940
    },
    {
      "id": "6a242ddc0000000000f14686",
      "text": "from [2026/06/05]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1780755932,
      "updated": 1780755932
    },
    {
      "id": "6a242ddc0000000000f14687",
      "text": "実というと、最近自作した「\"概念の出来\" を仕分けるカテゴリ」つくったの思い出した[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1780755932,
      "updated": 1780755951
    },
    {
      "id": "6a242ddc0000000000f14688",
      "text": "\t[/stao/Concept Botany]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1780755932,
      "updated": 1780755932
    },
    {
      "id": "6a242ddc0000000000f14689",
      "text": " [種: 🌰 Seed → 芽: 🌱 Sprout → 苗: 🪴 Seedling → 木: 🌳 Tree → 実: 🍎 Fruit]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1780755932,
      "updated": 1780755932
    },
    {
      "id": "6a242ddc0000000000f1468a",
      "text": " 人に配れる（梅棹がいう知的生産＝ひとにわかるように提出する）のが苗",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1780755932,
      "updated": 1780755932
    },
    {
      "id": "6a242ddc0000000000f1468b",
      "text": " その先に、体系など「ちゃんとまとめたでかいやつ」があって、それが木",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1780755932,
      "updated": 1780755932
    },
    {
      "id": "6a242ddc0000000000f1468c",
      "text": " \t木をつくれると、そこからさらに美味しいサブ概念（実）が色々出てくる",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1780755932,
      "updated": 1780755932
    },
    {
      "id": "6a242ddc0000000000f1468d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1780755932,
      "updated": 1780755932
    },
    {
      "id": "6a242df90000000000f1468e",
      "text": "[zatsma.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1780755962,
      "updated": 1780755962
    },
    {
      "id": "6a242dfa0000000000f1468f",
      "text": " [/stao/Concept Botany]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1780755962,
      "updated": 1780755962
    },
    {
      "id": "6a242dfa0000000000f14690",
      "text": "  すき👍",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1780755962,
      "updated": 1780755962
    },
    {
      "id": "6a242dfa0000000000f14691",
      "text": "  [Tekenote]が生きていたらノートの分類に活かせただろうな",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1780755962,
      "updated": 1780755962
    },
    {
      "id": "6a242dfa0000000000f14692",
      "text": "   [Tekenote.icon]のことは [デライトに似たツール]として度々思い出す",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1780755962,
      "updated": 1780973341
    },
    {
      "id": "6a242dfa0000000000f14696",
      "text": "\t\tスクショ残ってるプロジェクトがあった[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1780755962,
      "updated": 1780755962
    },
    {
      "id": "6a242dfa0000000000f14697",
      "text": "\t\t\t[/thinkandcreateteck/Tekenote]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1780755962,
      "updated": 1780755962
    },
    {
      "id": "6a242dfa0000000000f14698",
      "text": "\t\t\t thanks[zatsma.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1780755962,
      "updated": 1780755962
    },
